org.mitre.taxii.util
Some general utility classes.
Java library for TAXII.

This library provides:

  1. An object representation of TAXII Messages using JAXB.
  2. Serialization, deserialization, and validation of TAXII Messages.
  3. An HTTP/HTTPS TAXII Client using Apache's HTTP Components.
